         <abstract id="aspace_22749f66ac85db879100268d1fec94a2">The papers consist of correspondence, writings, and research materials used by Eliza D. Pierson, primarily in the compilation of a history of the S. S. Seward Institute of Florida, New York.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
